OL,3,CDoctors warn of 'threat to patient
OL,4,Csafety' over elderly people stuck in
OL,5,CA&E
OL,7,FSenior doctors have warned of an
OL,8,F"alarming threat to patient safety"
OL,9,Fafter figures showed more than a
OL,10,Fmillion elderly people endure long
OL,11,Fwaits in A&E ` and the older they are,
OL,12,Fthe more likely they are to experience
OL,13,Fit.
OL,15,FA report from the Royal College of
OL,16,FEmergency Medicine (RCEM), shared with
OL,17,Fthe PA news agency, shows that rising
OL,18,Fnumbers of elderly and frail people
OL,19,Fare stuck in A&E, often on trolleys in
OL,20,Fcorridors.
