OL,4,Csafety' over elderly people stuck in
OL,5,CA&E
OL,7,FFigures obtained by RCEM via the
OL,8,FFreedom of Information Act show that
OL,9,F1.15 million people aged 60 and over
OL,10,Fwaited more than 12 hours to be
OL,11,Ftransferred, admitted or discharged in
OL,12,FEngland's major A&E departments last
OL,13,Fyear.
OL,15,FThis is a jump from the 991,068 in
OL,16,F2023 and about three times the figure
OL,17,Ffor 2019, when 305,619 were affected.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
