OL,7,FIts Quality Improvement Programme
OL,8,F(QIP) study received data from 149
OL,9,Femergency departments involving 24,865
OL,10,Fpatients.
OL,12,FAmong patients over 75, the research
OL,13,Ffound insufficient screening for three
OL,14,Fcommon conditions which frequently
OL,15,Faffect older people.
OL,17,FAlthough there have been some
OL,18,Fimprovements, the report found:
