OL,7,FThe report recommended changes,
OL,8,Fincluding "front door frailty
OL,9,Fscreening" in every A&E. This is
OL,10,Falready being introduced across
OL,11,FScotland.
OL,13,FDr Adrian Boyle, president of the
OL,14,FRCEM, said, "The healthcare system is
OL,15,Ffailing our most vulnerable patients `
OL,16,Fmore than a million last year.
OL,18,F"These people are our parents,
OL,19,Fgrandparents, great-grandparents.
