OL,7,F"They aren't receiving the level of
OL,8,Fcare they need, as they endure the
OL,9,Flongest stays in our emergency
OL,10,Fdepartments, often suffering degrading
OL,11,Fand dehumanising corridor care.
OL,13,F"It's an alarming threat to patient
OL,14,Fsafety. We know long stays are
OL,15,Fdangerous, especially for those who
OL,16,Fare elderly, and puts people's lives
OL,17,Fat risk.
