OL,7,F"As our QIP highlights, more needs to
OL,8,Fbe done to improve their care ` vital
OL,9,Ftests need to get under way as soon as
OL,10,Fthey arrive to inform the care they
OL,11,Fneed and mitigate the risk of another
OL,12,Fvisit to the emergency department.
OL,14,F"There are good pockets of practice,
OL,15,Fand emergency medicine clinicians are
OL,16,Ftrying their best to deliver the care
OL,17,Fthey need.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
