OL,7,F"It's the system that's the issue and
OL,8,Fwill continue to disproportionally
OL,9,Faffect older people unless governments
OL,10,Facross the UK make A&E a political
OL,11,Fpriority."
OL,13,FDr Anu Mitra, project lead of RCEM's
OL,14,Fcare of older people QIP, said: "Older
OL,15,Fpeople make up a large proportion of
OL,16,Fattendances to the emergency
OL,17,Fdepartment, bringing greater health
OL,18,Fcomplexities and evolving care needs.
