OL,7,F"In the backdrop of worsening crowding
OL,8,Fand increasing long stays, emergency
OL,9,Fclinicians need to ensure they
OL,10,Fmaintain the basic elements of care
OL,11,Fand comfort for older patients.
OL,13,F"It's been encouraging to see that,
OL,14,Fdespite the challenging environments
OL,15,Femergency medicine clinicians are
OL,16,Fworking in, there has already been
OL,17,Fimprovements in ensuring these
OL,18,Fpatients are receiving the assessments
OL,19,Fthey need.
