OL,7,F"It's vital we continue this work for
OL,8,Fthis vulnerable patient cohort to meet
OL,9,Ftheir needs and provide the level of
OL,10,Fcare they deserve."
OL,12,FDr Nick Murch, president of the
OL,13,FSociety for Acute Medicine, said:
OL,14,F"This situation, where over a million
OL,15,Folder patients are known to have
OL,16,Fendured prolonged periods of over 12
OL,17,Fhours in emergency departments,
OL,18,Ffrequently in unsuitable and
OL,19,Fundignified settings such as
OL,20,Fcorridors, is a matter of grave
OL,21,Fconcern.
