OL,7,F"It is clear that, despite the
OL,8,Fconsiderable dedication and hard work
OL,9,Fof multidisciplinary teams including
OL,10,Femergency medicine, acute medicine and
OL,11,Facute frailty services, these extended
OL,12,Fwaiting times signify a profound
OL,13,Ffailure within our healthcare system.
OL,15,F"We must ensure that 12-hour waits in
OL,16,Femergency departments again become an
OL,17,Finfrequent exception rather than the
OL,18,Fnorm."
