OL,7,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,8,Fspokesman said: "It is unacceptable
OL,9,Fthat older people are waiting up to 12
OL,10,Fhours or more in A&E.
OL,12,F"This Government is investing #26
OL,13,Fbillion in the NHS and social care
OL,14,Fover the next two years, has ended the
OL,15,Fresident doctor strikes so staff are
OL,16,Fon the front line, and is committed to
OL,17,Fcutting A&E waiting times so patients
OL,18,Fare seen faster.
